OL,5,G0345 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FSexual harassment raises its ugly
OL,7,     Fhead in the newsroom - but for
OL,8,     Fonce its not Henry's. Meanwhile,
OL,9,     FDamien is busy invading every bit
OL,10,     Fof privacy he can to track down a
OL,11,     FNazi war criminal.
OL,12,G0410 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,13,     FGus introduces Jill, a newly
OL,14,     Fqualified newsreader, as the
OL,15,     Fyouthful face of Globelink's
OL,16,     Fimage. But Henry and Sally
OL,17,     Fdiscover she may become its only
OL,18,     Fface.
